News Releases, Media Advisories

April 7, 2003

ATTENTION WIRE SERVICES, DAYBOOK EDITORS:
FINAL AUDIT REPORT ON
JOHN SULLIVAN FOR CONGRESS
The Federal Election Commission has made available the final audit report on John Sullivan for Congress (OK 1st District). This audit covers the period of April 13, 2001 through March 31, 2002.

Contact: FEC Press Office (202) 694-1220, 999 E Street, NW
title: FEC Releases Final Audit Report on John Sullivan for Congress
